headline: Pharma Stock Roundup: LLY's New Deal, GSK & SNY's Pipeline Updates
summary: LLY to acquire SiteOne for up to $1 billion. GSK's antibiotic study ends early for efficacy. MRNA loses H5 flu vaccine funding, while SNY sees mixed COPD data.
